0-best-albums-of-the-nineties-20110427/beck-odelay-20110517 |website=Rolling Stone |accessdate=July 11, 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20170709053553/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-best-albums-of-the-nineties-20110427/beck-odelay-20110517 |archivedate=July 9, 2017 }}</ref>\n|2011\n|align=\"center\"|8\n|-\n|''[[Sounds (magazine)|Sounds]]''\n|United Kingdom\n|The 50 Best Albums of the 1990s\n|2009\n|align=\"center\"|37\n|-\n|rowspan=2|''[[The Source (magazine)|The Source]]''\n|rowspan=9|United States\n|The 100 Best Rap Albums of All Time\n|1998\n|align=\"center\"|*\n|-\n|The Critics Top 100 Black Music Albums of All Time<ref>[http://www.trevornelson.com/nonflash/top100.asp Trevornelson.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204222100/http://www.trevornelson.com/nonflash/top100.asp |date=February 4, 2012 }}</ref>\n|2006\n|align=\"center\"|8\n|-\n|rowspan=3|''[[Spin (magazine)|Spin]]''\n|Top 90 Albums of the 90s\n|1999\n|align=\"center\"|27\n|-\n|Top 100 (+5) Albums of the Last 20 Years\n|2005\n|align=\"center\"|30\n|-\n|The 125 Best Albums of the Past 25 Years\n|2010\n|align=\"center\"|43\n|-\n|''[[Time (magazine)|Time]]''\n|Top 100 Albums of All Time\n|2006\n|align=\"center\"|*\n|-\n|rowspan=2|''[[Vibe (magazine)|Vibe]]''\n|100 Essential Albums of the 20th Century\n|1999\n|align=\"center\"|*\n|-\n|150 Albums That Define the Vibe Era (1992\u20132007)\n|2007\n|align=\"center\"|*\n|-\n|''[[Village Voice]]''\n|Albums of the Year\n|1994\n|align=\"center\"|38\n|-\n|[[VPRO]]\n|[[Netherlands]]\n|299 Nominations of the Best Album of All Time\n|2006\n|align=\"center\"|*\n|}\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| extra_column    = Producer(s)\n\n| title1          = Intro\n| writer1         = {{hlist|[[The Notorious B.I.G.|Christopher Wallace]]|[[Sean Combs]]}}\n| extra1          = [[Sean Combs|Sean \"Puffy\" Combs]]\n| length1         = 3:24\n\n| title2          = [[Things Done Changed]]\n| writer2         = {{hlist|