perfly\" by [[Curtis Mayfield]]\n*\"[[Rapper's Delight]]\" by [[Sugarhill Gang]]\n*\"Top Billin'\" by [[Audio Two]]\n*\"Tha Shiznit\" by [[Snoop Doggy Dogg]]\n\n'''Things Done Changed'''\n*\"California My Way\" by [[The Main Ingredient (band)|The Main Ingredient]]\n*\"Summer Breeze\" by The Main Ingredient\n*\"Vapors\" by [[Biz Markie]]\n*\"Lil Ghetto Boy\" by [[Dr. Dre]]\n\n'''Gimme the Loot'''\n*\"Coldblooded\" by [[James Brown]]\n*\"Singing in the Morning\" by [[Ohio Players|The Ohio Players]] (Later removed following a lawsuit.)<ref name=bryantimes />\n*\"Throw Ya Gunz\" by [[Onyx (group)|Onyx]]\n*\"What They Hittin' Foe?\" by [[Ice Cube]]\n*\"Just to Get a Rep\" by [[Gang Starr]]\n*\"Scenario (Remix)\" by [[A Tribe Called Quest]]\n\n'''Machine Gun Funk'''\n*\"Something Extra\" by [[Black Heat]]\n*\"Up for the Down Stroke\" by [[The Horny Horns]] (Later removed following a lawsuit.)<ref name=bryantimes />\n*\"Chief Rocka\" by [[Lords of the Underground]]\n\n'''Warning'''\n*\"[[Walk On By (song)|Walk on By]]\" by [[Isaac Hayes]]\n\n'''Ready to Die'''\n*\"Hospital Prelude of Love Theme\" by [[Willie Hutch]]\n*\"Yes, I'm Ready\" by [[Barbara Mason]]\n*\"Ain't No Half Steppin'\" by [[Big Daddy Kane]]\n*\"Two to the Head\" by [[Kool G Rap]] & DJ Polo\n*\"Check It Out\" by [[Grand Puba]]\n*\"Singing in the Morning\" by Ohio Players (Later removed following a lawsuit.)<ref name=bryantimes />\n\n'''One More Chance'''\n*\"Hydra\" by [[Grover Washington, Jr.]]\n*\"Stay With Me\" by [[Debarge]]\n\n{{col-2}}\n\n'''Fuck Me (Interlude)'''\n*\"[[Feenin']]\" by [[Jodeci]]\n\n'''The What'''\n*\"Can't Say Enough About Mom\" by [[Leroy Hutson]]\n*\"Overnight Sensation\" by Avalanche\n\n'''Juicy'''\n*\"Juicy Fruit (\"Fruity\" Instrumental Mix)\" by [[Mtume]]\n\n'''Everyday Struggle'''\n*\"Either Way\" by [[Dave Grusin]] \n*\"Don't Change Your Love\" by [[Five Stairsteps|The Five Stairsteps]]\n\n'''Big Poppa'''\n*\"Between the Sheets\" by [[The Isley Brothers]]\n*\"Dolly My Baby (Ba